    public abstract class RestrictionsContainerAImpl
extends ElementAImpl
implements RestrictionsContainerA
    An implementation of the model object 'Container A'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Device Type Restrictions
    • Device Restrictions
    • Location Restrictions
    • Area Restrictions
    • Power Source Restrictions
    • Task Atomic Restrictions
    • Task Symmetry Restrictions
    • Input Synchronicity Restriction
    • Connection Restrictions
    • Connection Type Restrictions
    • Segregations Restrictions
    • Subrestrictions
    • Timedelayrestrictions
